==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Launce
<hw>Launce</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It. <ets>lance</ets>, L.
<ets>lanx</ets>, <ets>lancis</ets>, plate, scale of a balance. Cf.
<er>Balance</er>.]</ety> <def>A balance.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Fortune all in equal <qex>launce</qex> doth sway.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

